We were a band for almost three years and we didn't publish a record until Andy (Andrew Woods) died.
There's been a lot of frustration for the fact that it lasted so little and the most important thing is that we're still very friends with Bruce (Fairweather) and Greg (Gilmore) who started in the band with us and when I listen to a song or I see a picture I think about the amazing person Andy was and how he made me laugh, it was always a pleasure to work, laugh, talk about music, football and much more with him.
