Yes, the production sent us videos with different proposals and this one was the band we liked the most, so we look forward to seeing what Las Robertas can offer live and it must be very entertaining.
What do you always change Yello Ledbetter's lyrics for?
This is a question for Ed (Eddie Vedder), so I don't know.
